PN,30801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FMore than a million people with heart
OL,8,Fdisease are to be prescribed the
OL,9,Fweight loss jab Wegovy to prevent them
OL,10,Ffrom having heart attacks or strokes.
OL,12,FThe NHS's spending watchdog, the
OL,13,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,14,FExcellence (Nice), has given the green
OL,15,Flight to giving semaglutide to
OL,16,Foverweight and obese patients living
OL,17,Fwith certain heart and circulatory
OL,18,Fconditions to cut their risk of a
OL,19,Fmajor cardiovascular event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FSold under the brand name Wegovy and
OL,8,Fmade by Novo Nordisk, the weekly jab
OL,9,Fis a type of drug called a GLP-1
OL,10,Freceptor agonist which slows down how
OL,11,Fquickly food is digested, leading to
OL,12,Fweight loss.
OL,14,FNice said that clinical trials have
OL,15,Falso indicted that the drug works
OL,16,Fdirectly on the heart and blood
OL,17,Fvessels, not just through weight loss,
OL,18,Fas it approved the jab for a new
OL,19,Fpurpose.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FIt is expected that 1.2 million people
OL,8,Facross England could benefit.
OL,10,FNew guidance says the treatment can be
OL,11,Fused by patients with a body mass
OL,12,Findex (BMI) score of 27 or over in
OL,13,Faddition to other medicines, such as
OL,14,Fstatins, and alongside a reduced
OL,15,Fcalorie diet and increased exercise to
OL,16,Fprevent heart attacks and strokes.
OL,18,FThe move means there will be a rapid
OL,19,Fexpansion of people eligible to take
OL,20,Fthe drugs on the health service.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FSemaglutide is already available on
OL,8,Fthe NHS in England as a treatment
OL,9,Foption for people with obesity, it is
OL,10,Falso available under the different
OL,11,Fbrand name Ozempic for the treatment
OL,12,Fof type 2 diabetes.
OL,14,FNice said that evidence from a
OL,15,Fclinical trial shows the injection
OL,16,Freduces the risk of a heart attack,
OL,17,Fstroke or cardiovascular death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FIt said the study suggests that the
OL,8,Fbenefit was seen even before patients
OL,9,Flost a significant amount of weight,
OL,10,Fwhich suggests the drug works on the
OL,11,Fheart and blood vessels.
OL,13,FThere was a 20% reduced risk of a
OL,14,Fmajor heart event among the 17,604
OL,15,Fpeople who took part in the study.
OL,17,FNice said that its evaluation shows
OL,18,Fthe treatment is "cost effective" for
OL,19,FNHS use.
OL,26,@zD@ROUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FHealth service officials said the
OL,8,Ftreatment is set to be available on
OL,9,Fthe NHS "within months".
OL,11,F"We know that people who have already
OL,12,Fhad a heart attack or stroke are
OL,13,Fliving with real fear that it could
OL,14,Fhappen again," said Helen Knight,
OL,15,Fdirector of medicines evaluation at
OL,16,FNice.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@WO]sD@AOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,F"The evidence from the clinical trial
OL,8,Fis compelling. It showed that people
OL,9,Ftaking semaglutide alongside their
OL,10,Fexisting heart medicines were
OL,11,Fsignificantly less likely to have
OL,12,Fanother heart attack or stroke."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FHelen Williams, national clinical
OL,8,Fdirector for cardiovascular disease
OL,9,Fprevention at NHS England, added: "For
OL,10,Fmore than a million people at high
OL,11,Frisk of heart attack and stroke, this
OL,12,Ftreatment on the NHS could be life-
OL,13,Fchanging ` offering a powerful new way
OL,14,Fto protect their hearts and improve
OL,15,Ftheir health.
OL,17,F"We know that people who have already
OL,18,Fhad a heart attack or stroke face a
OL,19,Fmuch higher risk of having another.
OL,26,@qD@cOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,F"Used alongside a healthy diet and
OL,8,Fregular exercise, semaglutide could
OL,9,Fhelp prevent thousands of future major
OL,10,Fcardiovascular events and give many
OL,11,Fpeople the chance at a longer and
OL,12,Fhealthier life."
OL,14,FHealth minister Sharon Hodgson said:
OL,15,F"Weight loss drugs are proving to be a
OL,16,Fgame changer in tackling obesity.
OL,18,F"Extending their use for people who
OL,19,Falso suffer from cardiovascular
OL,20,Fdisease will be a life saver."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@PO]wD@AOUzD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FDr Sonya Babu-Narayan, clinical
OL,8,Fdirector at the British Heart
OL,9,FFoundation, said: "So-called 'weight
OL,10,Floss drugs' like semaglutide have
OL,11,Fproven benefits beyond reducing the
OL,12,Fnumber on the scales ` they are now
OL,13,Fconsidered important medicines for
OL,14,Fpreventing deadly heart attacks and
OL,15,Fstrokes.
OL,17,F"Today's guidance will no doubt help
OL,18,Fsave lives as cardiovascular disease
OL,19,Fis still one of the country's biggest
OL,20,Fkillers."
OL,26,@qD@SOUyD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FJuliet Bouverie, chief executive of
OL,8,Fthe Stroke Association, said: "We
OL,9,Falways encourage people to reduce
OL,10,Ftheir risk of stroke by maintaining a
OL,11,Fhealthy weight, but we understand this
OL,12,Fcan be a challenge for some.
OL,14,F"As stroke survivors live with the
OL,15,Fworrying threat of further strokes,
OL,16,Fit's vital they have options to help
OL,17,Fprevent that from happening, which
OL,18,Fsuit their own circumstances.
OL,26,@pD@_OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,F"As many survivors can be left with
OL,8,Fdisabilities which reduce movement,
OL,9,Fweight loss medication could be a
OL,10,Fsuitable option for them, when
OL,11,Frecommended by a medical professional."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775009000
OL,3,C1m to get 'life-changing' weight loss
OL,4,Cdrugs to prevent heart attacks and
OL,5,Cstrokes
OL,7,FSebnem Avsar Tuna, general manager for
OL,8,FNovo Nordisk UK, said the move was an
OL,9,F"important step", adding: "It means
OL,10,Fclinicians in England now have access
OL,11,Fto a further treatment that Nice has
OL,12,Ffound to be cost effective, the first
OL,13,Fand only GLP-1 receptor agonist proven
OL,14,Fto reduce the risk of heart attack,
OL,15,Fstroke or cardiovascular death in this
OL,16,Fhigh risk population."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]qD@[OUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
